settings.description: I wanted to do a very complete level 0-0

Mario traverses through the 4 elements of Water, Earth, Fire, and Air! Water room is a bit buggy!
Difficulty: 2/5
Just a simple traditional level with note blocks, try to find all 5 e-Coins!
Luigi has teamed up with bowser to take over the mushroom kingdom using the advanced P-wing, Mario must take the advanced P-wing from the chest to halfway stop the invasion.
Suppose it's time for an old washed up mario flash level maker to step foot into a new light... with a new honestly great level making program as well! hopefully this level's fun too!
